            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# CodexPocketMac 0.1.4

- Improve Codex CLI discovery so the Mac bridge can find executables installed in standard Homebrew and system paths, even when the app launch environment has a limited PATH.
- Refresh the CLI setup guidance and TestFlight release documentation links.
- Keep the release on build 9, matching the uploaded iPhone companion build for this release candidate.
]]></description>
