            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# CodexPocketMac 0.1.2

- Improve post-build deployment so Xcode can auto-detect a single connected iPhone and require an explicit target only when multiple devices are attached.
- Continue the unreleased source changes since 0.1.1, including plan transcript parsing, runtime stability improvements, macOS language-following settings, and thread preview polish.
]]></description>
